<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">竜彦</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「そういうことが続くと、どうなるか分るかい？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">和彦</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「いえ―」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">竜彦</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「胸ン中、からっぽになるのさ」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">和彦</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「―」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">竜彦</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「魂がうつろになるんだ」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">和彦</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「―」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">竜彦</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「なにかを、心から好きになるなんて事もなくなっちまう」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">和彦</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「（うなずく）」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">竜彦</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「カメラ売り払ってね」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">和彦</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「（うなずく）」</sentence>
