</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「―」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">竜彦</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「煙でもいい（と煙ののぼる空を見る）」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">和彦</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「名前、聞いてもいいですか？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
